{"tid":588355,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家] 某動物園為左節省成本竟然不建圍欄直接用紙皮封死動物區","createTime":"2018-03-11T07:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T07:11:28.000Z","uid":59328,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a8873bc1bee03ed40954b16152e92a119cb15c8b","tid":588355,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:05:46.000Z","msg":"雖然現在遊戲經常被批評為過於暴力，下下殺人屠龍，但其實如果大家唔想打機搞到成個mon都係紅色的話，可以輕鬆玩下D沙盒遊戲。例如動物園大亨，大家可以親親大自然，見識一下稀有新奇動物。可惜我唔夠老屎無玩過1,2代，再down翻開心版時已經發覺隻game垃圾係win10 boot唔到，有開心版都無用，惟有玩動物園大亨2013年版本。其實隻game早係2013年xbox推出，不過係2017年更係PC再推出「威力加強版」，加入了南美及澳洲動物，更聲稱有超過200隻動物比你gotta catch them all！不過動物園大亨2013可否延續1,2代的經典呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/131658_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F131658_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=bc54a6b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一入到去有教學模式、劇本模式、挑戰模式同沙盒模式，為左節省時間今次我決定揀沙盒模式。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/131958_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F131958_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=e752dd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哇！有成20個國家比你選擇，咁我呢D愛國愛港人士當然選擇強國動物園啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/132735_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F132735_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=269b4ca8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/132548_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F132548_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=aa2171fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吐嘈1：雖然有成20個地區選擇，但其實個個地區都是一樣，所有地區都只是一塊<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">長方形空地，並沒有任何高低起伏、高山、河川、海洋等自然地理變化</span></strong>，惟一不同的僅只是背景的區別。(上：中國動物園；下：美國動物園)<br />\n<br />\n咁要起動物園當然要有動物啦，首先當然要揀塊空地去起圍欄先。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/133353_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F133353_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=a618d684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/133514_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F133514_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=f3810600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吐嘈2：Sorry！呢個係我見過最古怪的動物園，原來起動物園係唔洗起圍欄，你只需要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">揀生態環境，同大小</span></strong>(小:3隻動物；中：6隻動物；大：10隻動物，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所有生態環境都有容量限制</strong></span>，唔洗諗住可以整個百獅巢穴咁大氣派)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/134710_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F134710_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=bdc20cde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吐嘈3：最後我選擇了小型熱帶生態區，放了兩隻孟加拉虎係入面。其實所謂的揀生態環境，就好似揀罐頭食品咁，所有野已然整好預設曬，你<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不能整高低地型、換地板、整水池，甚至不能放上任何花草樹木，連本來那個開放式低圍欄也不能調高換上</span></strong>(你確定我們身處的地方安全嗎？)<br />\n<br />\n而係動物滿足度方面，只要你選好地型同有足夠同種類動物(大部份只需要2隻，但有一部份如大象要求要3隻，而袋鼠甚至要求4隻)，那麼就只需要提供食物(<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">所有動物不需飲水</span></strong>)，灑水器沖涼同各種玩具遊玩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/135505_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F135505_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=465f8303&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/135535_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F135535_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=7e640870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/135612_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F135612_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=dba7e544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吐嘈4：連<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">食物、灑水器同玩具都要set係指定位置</span></strong>，仲要係正角落邊沿位，自由大倒退！(上：肉食、中：曬水器、下：磨爪柱)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/140603_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F140603_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=cc01fd87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講返動物，官方聲稱有超過200隻動物！<br />\n<br />\n吐嘈5：但其實唔計小型動物，只有14種大型動物(羊駝、羚羊、熊、黑猩猩、美洲獅、大象、長頸鹿、河馬、美洲豹、袋鼠、獅子、大羊駝、犀牛、老虎)，所謂超過200隻動物只是<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">共用模組，一種動物改下名字分成聽都未聽過的亞種</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/141801_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F141801_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=f1626fa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連大象都有成6隻咁多...<br />\n<br />\n共用模組都算啦，起碼棕熊同北極熊顏色不同，極易看穿，但問題遊戲有太多<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">外表極相似甚至一樣不同亞種的動物</span></strong>，讓人感覺久缺誠意！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/142826_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F142826_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=e3edd139&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左：非洲大象；右：婆羅洲大象，難分真與假<br />\n<br />\n我知微軟廢過Sony任天堂，但既然整得長頸鹿，可唔可以整返隻斑馬出來呀？係咪當玩家on9架？<br />\n<br />\n最後講多一句，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">動物只能放在生態罐頭裏</span></strong>，而不能放在世界任意區域，所以再無放老虎咬人咁好玩啦！<br />\n<br />\n講完動物講道路，這個遊戲連道路都唔需要起，微軟會發揮佢精密的高科技AI巧妙地自動連接道路...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/143615_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F143615_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=0ea258ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吐嘈6：全自動道路系統(你<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只能在黃色區域中起道路</span></strong>)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/144010_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F144010_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=6fc81f18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果你想拐彎抹角的話可以加入迴轉處作為中繼點(咁點解一開始唔直接比玩家自制道路呢？)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/144408_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F144408_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=24b7da57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後講埋食物店，食物店竟然可以比玩家有自訂功能？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/144516_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F144516_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=f2075d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吐嘈7：但原來所謂的自訂功能，只是比你<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">加長椅(只有長椅仲要又係藍色指定位置)</span></strong>，我想加D花裝飾下環境都唔得。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/144926_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F144926_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=580eb68e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n惟一例外是廣場空地中間可加入噴水池或雕像...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/145118_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F145118_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=2f8b4d8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吐嘈8：而另外為左唔想大家有數學恐懼症，所有售價，包括門票、食品、紀念品店等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一律變成為高、中、低</strong></span>，變得十分抽象又陌生...<br />\n<br />\n另一方面這個遊戲亦可以讓你而遊客視覺，自制人物感受一下親親大自然的樂趣，但呢隻唔係模擬市民<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撞面情況非常嚴重</span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/11/145822_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F11%2F145822_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=23893611&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吐嘈9：笑甚麼笑，你都只是喬伊小姐！<br />\n<br />\n因為字數限制，講多一句如果你想買一隻game單純感受一下養動物的樂趣，這次的動物園大亨係可以接受的，但如果你想要一隻次世代的動物園大亨續作的話，我只能講-伏伏伏伏伏...<br />\n<br />\n有乜野再加落去再講，仲有太多伏位。"},{"pid":"c89c86c7322c6936430648623ce18c2adf951b6d","tid":588355,"uid":30213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"吐乜撚嘢嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa3b328ad944e66922b774a4bf3be1634237c8ec","tid":588355,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T07:11:28.000Z","msg":"笑咗"}]}